JUBILE-R.BK.summary: Jubilee Enterprise Public Company Limited operates as a retailer and wholesaler of diamond jewelry in Thailand. The company provides rings, earrings, pendants, brooches, and bangles for women; and rings for men. It also offers its products through online. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.

PDJ-R.BK.summary: Pranda Jewelry Public Company Limited engages in the production, distribution, and retail of fine jewelry. The company offers gold and silver jewelry, and brass and fashion costume jewelry products under the Prima Gold, Prima Diamond, Prima Art, Julia, Merii, and Gemondo brands. It is also involved in dormitory rental activities. The company operates retail and franchise outlets in Asia and the Middle East, as well as offers its products through department stores, chain stores, websites, TV, and catalogs. It operates 8 outlets in Vietnam and 24 outlets in Indonesia. The company was formerly known as Pranda Design Company Limited. Pranda Jewelry Public Company Limited was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.

SAWANG-R.BK.summary: Sawang Export Public Company Limited engages in the manufacture and distribution of precious stones and jewelry in Thailand, Europe, Australia, the United States, and internationally. The company offers jewelry accessories, including rings, pendants, earrings, and necklaces made with 8k, 9k, 10k, 14k, and 18k gold or silver consisting of diamond and color stones. It also provides diamond, precious, semi-precious, and created stones; color stones, such as rubies, and natural blue and yellow sapphires, as well as synthetic stones; and gold and silver jewelry sets. The company offers its products through department and online stores under the Beawelry and Silver Star 7 brands. It also exports its products. Sawang Export Public Company Limited was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.
